{"tid":1353031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實元朗有好多中產，今次鄉黑搞埋佢地，我地出嚟佢地都會支持","createTime":"2019-07-23T01:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T06:24:35.000Z","uid":215265,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"94b7d2a3328aac2f05ce22f6f998a2aaf76fd61d","tid":1353031,"uid":215265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:31:10.000Z","msg":"特別係YOHO 果班，我敢話你地出嚟佢地實支持<br />\n佢哋都唔想活喺恐懼之中<br />\n今次係要攞正牌迫政府鏟除黑惡<br />\n正如之前屯門公園同紅土迫到民建聯都要發聲<br />\n<br />\n出面有咁多post 叫人唔好入元朗，好大機會係有人怕搞亂選舉步署，哩幾年建制好落力做，尤其YOHO，日日走出嚟派傳單，又成日爭取ABC bla bla bla，佢哋都怕一Q清袋<br />\n<br />\n大家出嚟行佢地都無得唔回應<br />\n做好文宣踢走王威信，郭靜然，莊展銘"},{"pid":"d4f5ca4494b1f378c919c7c5146b90133dde3461","tid":1353031,"uid":215265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:32:30.000Z","msg":"唔好屈服白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n推啊！"},{"pid":"43d9878f4bb8b4c482cafcd1e797e4e69d25e439","tid":1353031,"uid":76068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:32:33.000Z","msg":"廢除丁權"},{"pid":"1ae723ef679cc391285e42b7b51e919520a47bba","tid":1353031,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:32:45.000Z","msg":"叫醒身邊人<br />\n與手足同行<br />\nSorry Hong Kong is closed today<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1350179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1350179</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ec6021bb0d6feb85905865523c01681b37db5f61","tid":1353031,"uid":57328,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Y8UyEFx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY8UyEFx.png&h=d3096026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗勢力分佈圖，有唔明隨時回答"},{"pid":"047787b1d6a5a59bd7053cf540087fd0a93a0099","tid":1353031,"uid":215265,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T01:33:17.000Z","msg":"當我求下你地<br />\n<br />\n唔好放棄屯元天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.g